{"vv80:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv80:0.2":"Purisavimana ","vv80:0.3":"Sunikkhittavagga ","vv80:0.4":"6. Gopalavimanavatthu ","vv80:1.1":"“Disvana devam patipucchi bhikkhu, ","vv80:1.2":"Ucce vimanamhi ciratthitike; ","vv80:1.3":"Amuttahatthabharanam yasassim, ","vv80:1.4":"Dibbe vimanamhi yathapi candima. ","vv80:2.1":"Alankato malyadharo suvattho, ","vv80:2.2":"Sukundali kappitakesamassu; ","vv80:2.3":"Amuttahatthabharano yasassi, ","vv80:2.4":"Dibbe vimanamhi yathapi candima. ","vv80:3.1":"Dibba ca vina pavadanti vaggum, ","vv80:3.2":"Atthatthaka sikkhita sadhurupa; ","vv80:3.3":"Dibba ca kanna tidasacara ulara, ","vv80:3.4":"Naccanti gayanti pamodayanti. ","vv80:4.1":"Deviddhipattosi mahanubhavo, ","vv80:4.2":"Manussabhuto kimakasi punnam; ","vv80:4.3":"Kenasi evam jalitanubhavo, ","vv80:4.4":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv80:5.1":"So devaputto attamano, ","vv80:5.2":"…pe… ","vv80:5.3":"yassa kammassidam phalam. ","vv80:6.1":"“Aham manussesu manussabhuto, ","vv80:6.2":"Sangamma rakkhissam paresam dhenuyo; ","vv80:6.3":"Tato ca aga samano mamantike, ","vv80:6.4":"Gavo ca mase agamamsu khaditum. ","vv80:7.1":"Dvayajja kiccam ubhayanca kariyam, ","vv80:7.2":"Iccevaham bhante tada vicintayim; ","vv80:7.3":"Tato ca sannam patiladdha yoniso, ","vv80:7.4":"Dadami bhanteti khipim anantakam. ","vv80:8.1":"So masakhettam turito avasarim, ","vv80:8.2":"Pura ayam bhanjati yassidam dhanam; ","vv80:8.3":"Tato ca kanho urago mahaviso, ","vv80:8.4":"Adamsi pade turitassa me sato. ","vv80:9.1":"Svaham attomhi dukkhena pilito, ","vv80:9.2":"Bhikkhu ca tam samam muncitvanantakam; ","vv80:9.3":"Ahasi kummasam mamanukampaya, ","vv80:9.4":"Tato cuto kalakatomhi devata. ","vv80:10.1":"Tadeva kammam kusalam katam maya, ","vv80:10.2":"Sukhanca kammam anubhomi attana; ","vv80:10.3":"Taya hi bhante anukampito bhusam, ","vv80:10.4":"Katannutaya abhivadayami tam. ","vv80:11.1":"Sadevake loke samarake ca, ","vv80:11.2":"Anno muni natthi tayanukampako; ","vv80:11.3":"Taya hi bhante anukampito bhusam, ","vv80:11.4":"Katannutaya abhivadayami tam. ","vv80:12.1":"Imasmim loke parasmim va pana, ","vv80:12.2":"Anno muni natthi tayanukampako; ","vv80:12.3":"Taya hi bhante anukampito bhusam, ","vv80:12.4":"Katannutaya abhivadayami tan”ti. ","vv80:13.1":"Gopalavimanam chattham. "}